WEBVTT

00:00:01.970 --> 00:00:07.969
Our sacred service is our sacrifice, our gift to Jehovah.

00:00:07.969 --> 00:00:09.970
But here's a key point.

00:00:09.970 --> 00:00:14.970
Before Jehovah looks at our gift, he looks at us.

00:00:14.970 --> 00:00:19.969
He must accept us first if he's to accept our gift.

00:00:19.969 --> 00:00:22.969
So here's the key question then.

00:00:22.969 --> 00:00:25.969
What does Jehovah look for in us?

00:00:25.969 --> 00:00:30.969
We're going to use three Bible examples to explore that question.

00:00:30.969 --> 00:00:36.969
Let's begin in the most holy of the tabernacle on the day of atonement.

