Leviticus chapter 16, the first time he enters the most holy on that day,

00:01:04.969 --> 00:01:09.969
he will then take the firehold of full of burning calls from the altar before Jehovah,

00:01:09.969 --> 00:01:15.969
to handfuls of fine perfumed incense, and he will bring them inside the curtain.

00:01:15.969 --> 00:01:19.969
He will also put the incense on the fire before Jehovah,

00:01:19.969 --> 00:01:23.969
and the cloud of the incense will envelop the ark cover, which is on the testimony,

00:01:23.969 --> 00:01:27.969
