00:01:27.969 --> 00:01:30.969
Clearly, from their last phrase,

00:01:30.969 --> 00:01:38.969
Jehovah needed to approve of the high priest and what he did if he was to accept the sin offering.

00:01:38.969 --> 00:01:44.209
He had to bring an incense.

00:01:44.209 --> 00:01:48.209
