00:02:18.210 --> 00:02:24.490
So what qualities was Jehovah looking for in the high priest?

00:02:24.490 --> 00:02:36.370
A humble, prayerful attitude, strict obedience to direction, moral and spiritual integrity.

00:02:36.370 --> 00:02:47.060
Everything on that day, the high priest and his sin offering, pictured Jesus Christ.

00:02:47.060 --> 00:02:51.060
So what can we learn from Jesus while he was on earth?

